citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on
9/3/2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee/registrant by phone calls to the cell and home phone numbers.
Knocked on the front door and garage door. Also submitted a text and got a response that the licensee was out of town
and would not be back until evening. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a
serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
